name: Chonk the Frog
description: A coin to celebrate the animations of chonk the frog! I have been creating animations across multiple social media accounts for the last few years. They are bright colourful and aim to bring joy to everyone! This project is to help interact with the 2million+ community and find ways to give back for all of their support! Chonk is simple and bright and fun and hopefully this project can be an extension of this
